{"tid":852054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就是愛韓系歐巴！洋男捧300萬整形 結果變...","createTime":"2018-10-07T14:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T14:37:13.000Z","uid":179810,"like":18,"dislike":205,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"f248d1e045795ab1948444bd6fbb6e27e2b422f7","tid":852054,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20181006001814-260809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20181006001814-260809&d=es60O2Uq%2FqKFSTxPdPysw%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ba1fd62e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20181006001814-260809</a><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-06/590/20181006001817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-06%2F590%2F20181006001817.jpg&h=8ce876b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n現代醫美發達，不少人都透過整形將自己身上不滿意的地方做修正，不過也有人因此走火入魔將自己整到連家人都認不出來。英國就有位名為Oli的男子，相當喜歡韓系潮流，後來更是花了大把鈔票把自己整成「韓系歐巴」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-06/590/20181006001818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-06%2F590%2F20181006001818.jpg&h=55c8641a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n根據了解，Oli第一次整形時就特地飛到韓國，並拿著南韓藝人朴智旻的照片，要求醫生把自己的鼻子整得跟朴智旻一樣高，此外他還抽脂、削骨、豐唇，希望自己徹頭徹尾變成一位歐巴。但後來Oli還是不滿意自己的臉，覺得自己的眼睛看起來還是像個西方男性，最後一次他帶著75000英鎊(約為台幣306萬)，要求醫生把他的眼型做成朴智旻的模樣，但由於眼部手術較精密，醫生也警告可能會失明，但Oli完全不怕，就是想要成為韓國歐巴。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-06/590/20181006001824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-06%2F590%2F20181006001824.jpg&h=3bea4d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n不過也有不少人覺得他整形前還比較好看。（圖／截取自《每日郵報》）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手術完成後Oli相當開心，直呼「我現在看起來像極了韓國人！」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但不少網友看過都覺得相當不像，甚至表明整形前的他好看多了，現在比較像是外星人或是骷髏。"},{"pid":"1fc227c36d512168b592c81dd0453bc9edac9728","tid":852054,"uid":182930,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"男Barbie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb430859f5a9b1e9a7f2e88eac10c15e44868a0","tid":852054,"uid":16061,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"1fc227c36d512168b592c81dd0453bc9edac9728","tid":852054,"uid":182930,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"男Barbie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"ken"},{"pid":"af2dd81d30e087743afdda867fa648d8f9c2cf03","tid":852054,"uid":59114,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國版蛇男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91b06e243f1bcbbafd7d33557796f47f7b4c2ca","tid":852054,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"6a4741a23ae8c40ffe4e00d6ab7d9019988a92e0","tid":852054,"uid":62409,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"自甘墜落"},{"pid":"65e19b0c9c5a1abb31ab31365a3e9cf5595d2508","tid":852054,"uid":165368,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"完全唔似朴智旻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba14853e88bf6430ed6d980216a2bdaa69717075","tid":852054,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"攞嚟衰"},{"pid":"bbaa5060babb421701c4b5b452ec16556f607730","tid":852054,"uid":115579,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"未整之前係咁食韓妹，整左連阿嬸都作嘔"},{"pid":"7021d